    <detaileddescription>
<para>QPushButton that controls visibility of the associated QLineEdit&apos;s contents (e.g., show/hide password).</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>line</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>QLineEdit whose contents are shown or hidden by this button. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>parent</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Optional parent widget. Emitted when the button action occurs, carrying the current text of the associated QLineEdit.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>The</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>current text of the associated QLineEdit. Handles the button activation state and updates the associated QLineEdit accordingly.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>checked</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The new checked/toggled state of the button. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
